    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, maintained to an exacting mechanical standard. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting a high-revving valvetrain and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous atmospheric response. The critical VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has undergone professional reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, preserving the communicative steering rack and balanced weight distribution. Free of rod bearing issues or underbody oxidation, this is a turn-key example for the purist collector.",
      "price": 47500.0,
