    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear or creasing, and the original interior scent remains. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. It has never seen rain or salt, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. Included are all original manuals, two master keys, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a collector-grade time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands the absolute best.",
